    "longBusinessSummary": "HVC Investment and Technology Joint Stock Company engages in the provision and installation of high-end amusement and recreational equipment. The company engages in the design, installation, and supply of entertainment equipment, such as swimming pools, art fountains, ice skating rinks, ocean aquarium, and water parks, as well as wastewater treatment and gaming equipment; electrical, light electrical, ventilation, and fire protection equipment; design and construction of amusement parks; and production of electric cabinets, wind pipes, and cable tray ladders. Its products portfolio includes high trill game, kids slide game, spiral slide, wave pool, smartpool equipment, ferris wheel, heating and sand filtration equipment for pools, pumps, smart filtration systems, chillers, cooling towers, cold glycol pumps, insulation foams, dehumidification, cold piping, and filtration and demineralization systems, as well as ice resurfacers, dasher boards, paint spraying packages, ice surface paints, ice edgers, ice skates, skate sharpening machines, glycol testers, shoe dryers, spa jacuzzi and sauna steam equipments, water treatment chemicals, spain water pump equipment. HVC Investment and Technology Joint Stock Company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
